00:31:38.580 --> 00:31:40.640
And it's basically great.

00:31:40.640 --> 00:31:45.570
Until DVD making technology
got way cheap, maybe

00:31:45.570 --> 00:31:46.680
even too cheap.

00:31:46.680 --> 00:31:49.090
And the problem now is that
there's a serious problem

00:31:49.090 --> 00:31:51.740
with piracy of Nollywood DVDs.

00:31:51.740 --> 00:31:54.176
So if you're a
filmmaker in Nigeria,

00:31:54.176 --> 00:31:55.800
you can actually have
a serious problem

00:31:55.800 --> 00:31:57.790
in terms of making money
to be able to create

00:31:57.790 --> 00:31:59.950
more great films.

00:31:59.950 --> 00:32:02.950
So the makers of Nollywood
saw this problem.

00:32:02.950 --> 00:32:05.240
But again, they also
saw an opportunity.

00:32:05.240 --> 00:32:08.220
Because there was a new trend
also happening in Nigeria.

00:32:08.220 --> 00:32:09.910
And yep, it's the
mobile phones again.

00:32:09.910 --> 00:32:12.430
Almost every adult in
Nigeria has a mobile phone,

00:32:12.430 --> 00:32:14.880
and smartphones are
growing really quickly too.

00:32:14.880 --> 00:32:18.510
They're also seeing a lot higher
rates of mobile data access,

00:32:18.510 --> 00:32:21.760
and a lot of adults in Nigeria
also get great WiFi service

00:32:21.760 --> 00:32:23.290
when they're at work, too.

00:32:23.290 --> 00:32:25.980
So this meant a new way
for Nollywood directors

00:32:25.980 --> 00:32:28.700
to distribute their films
to all of their fans.

00:32:28.700 --> 00:32:30.920
And so it's also easier
for Nollywood films

00:32:30.920 --> 00:32:34.070
to reach the global
fanbase more quickly.

00:32:34.070 --> 00:32:35.720
So people in Nigeria
are obviously

00:32:35.720 --> 00:32:37.650
fans, but also people
all over Africa,

00:32:37.650 --> 00:32:42.360
and Brazil is also a huge
market for Nollywood films too.

00:32:42.360 --> 00:32:45.280
So Afrinolly won the
Android Developer Challenge

00:32:45.280 --> 00:32:47.730
four years ago, in 2011.

00:32:47.730 --> 00:32:49.640
And the founders got
the idea for their app

00:32:49.640 --> 00:32:52.370
because they saw some data
on the top Google searches

00:32:52.370 --> 00:32:53.550
all over Africa.

00:32:53.550 --> 00:32:56.490
And a lot of them were searches
about Nollywood movies.

00:32:56.490 --> 00:33:00.470
But at the time, there was
no IMDb for African cinema,

00:33:00.470 --> 00:33:02.640
there really wasn't
anywhere to send people.

00:33:02.640 --> 00:33:04.290
So they decided to
create something,

00:33:04.290 --> 00:33:06.860
and they built Afrinolly to
make this information broadly

00:33:06.860 --> 00:33:07.940
available.

00:33:07.940 --> 00:33:10.510
So they won the big
prize here, $25,000,

00:33:10.510 --> 00:33:12.740
and they decided to invest
that money in marketing

00:33:12.740 --> 00:33:15.440
the new Afrinolly app.

00:33:15.440 --> 00:33:18.510
