00:33:21.950 --> 00:33:24.180
They're all based
in Lagos, Nigeria.

00:33:24.180 --> 00:33:26.940
And their technical team, five
people there on the right,

00:33:26.940 --> 00:33:29.270
are responsible for building
the Afrinolly app, as well

00:33:29.270 --> 00:33:33.670
as all of the technical services
that Afrinolly works with.

00:33:33.670 --> 00:33:35.900
So we said that Afrinolly
started out as a place

00:33:35.900 --> 00:33:38.580
to read about the latest
Nollywood news and gossip,

00:33:38.580 --> 00:33:40.800
